Debian-CBS installation CD-ROM

http://github.com/vladimir-ipatov/cbs

This is the Debian/GNU Linux custom CD-ROM, which helps to install
the complete multipurpose server in less than a 1 hour.

* Optimized and quet installer with predefined partitioning schemes
* Tune (automatically) system parameters for productivity
* Set up network services if you need.

Debian-CBS includes pre-tuned services:

* firewall: iptables-persistent
* transparent proxy: squid+squidguard
* traffic statistics: bandwidthd+lightsquid
* web server with site separation: nginx+php-fpm+mysql
* videoserver: zoneminder
* dns server with ddns support: bind9
* dhcp server with ddns support: isc-dhcp-server
* file server: samba
* domain controller: samba4
* mail server: exim4+dovecot
* bacula server: bacula-director-mysql+bacula-sd-mysql
* bacula agent: bacula-fd
* zabbix server: zabbix-mysql zabbix-frontend-php
* zabbix agent
* puppet server: puppetmaster
* terminal server: xrdp+x11rdp+lxde


To build the project you'll need Debian/GNU environment with these packages:
sharutils simple-cdd debhelper dpkg-dev

Read OVERVIEW next.
